QuestData.Title: Tooth and Claw
QuestData.Description: These wimps lugging wood around the jungle keep talking about how dangerous it is. You know, between the ravager den to the south or the raptors that stalk Zorammarsh - hey, even the beach creatures or podlings have teeth!$b$bWhat do you say you and I do a little hunting? Collect teeth from wild beasts. The bigger the beast, the more teeth. Meet me back here and we'll compare our haul!
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect $oa Tanaan Jungle Teeth from the various wildlife within Tanaan Jungle.
